{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SHELF/rbdsphereproxy", "tags": "rigidbodies"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["RBD Sphere Proxy"], "extent": [48, 69]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates a number of rigid bodies from SOP geometry, which use proxy geometry composed of adaptively-sized spheres."], "extent": [69, 192]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [192, 207], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool uses ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres"}, " to generate proxy geometry for the RBD objects.\nA compound collision shape built from many spheres can be much faster to simulate, particularly for concave geometry."], "extent": [207, 414]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is similar to the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/rbdconvexproxy", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Convex Proxy tool"], "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdconvexproxy"}, " on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " shelf. However, instead of generating a compound collision shape built from several convex hulls, it builds the shape from many spheres."], "extent": [414, 650]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rbdsphereproxy.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [650, 692]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using RBD Sphere Proxy"], "extent": [692, 733], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry to convert to an RBD sphere object."], "extent": [733, 797]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Optionally, define the pieces to be fractured. For example, using the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/shatter", "type": "link", "text": ["Shatter tool"], "fullpath": "/shelf/shatter"}, "."], "extent": [797, 905]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdsphereproxy", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdsphereproxy"}, {"scheme": "Shelf", "value": "rbdsphereproxy", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdsphereproxy"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab."], "extent": [905, 1004]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Modify the parameters of the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons"}, " SOP and the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres"}, " SOP, if necessary, to adjust the voxel size used and the maximum number of generated spheres."], "extent": [1004, 1197]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Switch the display flag to the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/xformpieces", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xformpieces"}, " SOP to see the original geometry transformed based on the motion of the proxy objects."], "extent": [1197, 1345]}], "container": true}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdpackedobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Packed Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}, " or ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "COMMON/openvdb", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/COMMON/openvdb"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres", "type": "link", "text": ["VDB to Spheres"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres"}, " help."], "extent": [1345, 1522]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1522, 1531], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/bulletrbdsolver", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/bulletrbdsolver"}], "extent": [1531, 1561]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}], "extent": [1561, 1590]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbfrompolygons"}], "extent": [1590, 1619]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/vdbtospheres"}], "extent": [1619, 1645]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/xformpieces", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xformpieces"}], "extent": [1645, 1670]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["RBD Sphere Proxy"], "summary": ["Creates a number of rigid bodies from SOP geometry, which use proxy geometry composed of adaptively-sized spheres."]}